76561198032587351,Recommended,242680,26795073,"Posted: 23 November, 2016",all,jetman28,"Nuclear Throne is one of those games where if you start playing it, it becomes hard to put down. I played the crap out of this online and off and I find it to have interesting new things to offer each time. It's fast pace and RNG keep it fresh, along with ridiculous mods that the community puts out. If you are a fan of punishment and post apocalyptic crazyness then this game is for you. If you aren't a fan of that then I am sure the soundtrack will pull you in as it has myself and many other players."
